name: Kim Minju
description:
Check out this My BMAC Page for more LORAs

This is still in early stage, im planning to change the dataset as the results does not really resemble the real person.

It is prohibited to use this Lora to make NSFW/18+ images

Works well with 2.5d models but not really well with photorealistic models

Recommended models: dalcefo realistic, lofi, lucky strike mix

Trigger word is "minju"

Recommended settings:

CFG scale = 4.5-7

steps = 20-40

Sampler = DPM SDE karras or DPM 2M++ karras

hires.fix = latent (or no hires.fix)

denoise = 0.5

If you use photorealistic model

CFG scale = 4-6

steps = 16-40

denoise = 0.35-0.5

Thank you
